Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: An overnight hero
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xw79
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Jul 1987
The Iran-Contra hearing's main witness becomes an unlikely hero to tens of thousands of Americans. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less